cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.ET, cs.PF 

Reasoning: 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes an optimization framework for coordinating voltage regulation in distribution systems, which falls under the domain of systems and control. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses a novel linearization method to convexify the optimization problem, which could be considered as an application of artificial intelligence techniques. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper may involve software engineering aspects such as implementation and testing of the proposed method. 
- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies): The paper deals with the integration of PV smart inverters in distribution systems, which could be considered as an emerging technology. 
- cs.PF (Performance): The paper aims to minimize voltage deviations and tap operations, which could be considered as performance metrics for voltage regulation in distribution systems.
